Wait a minute!

1041
01:28:22,664 --> 01:28:25,258
- What are you looking for?
- Buns.

1042
01:28:25,833 --> 01:28:27,391
I forgot them.

1043
01:28:27,702 --> 01:28:30,034
- You forgot the buns?
- Yeah.

1044
01:28:30,238 --> 01:28:32,069
How can you eat a hot dog
without a bun?

1045
01:28:32,340 --> 01:28:36,242
- It's not a hot dog without...
- Don't eat the fucking thing, then!

1046
01:28:36,878 --> 01:28:38,038
Shit!

1047
01:28:42,750 --> 01:28:44,411
It ain't bad.

1048
01:28:53,861 --> 01:28:55,123
Shit!

1049
01:28:58,599 --> 01:29:02,695
- I don't want no fucking hot dogs.
- He don't eat them without buns.

1050
01:29:26,160 --> 01:29:28,628
It's kind of like being at sea.

1051
01:29:31,933 --> 01:29:34,458
I was on a weather ship once...

1052
01:29:34,769 --> 01:29:36,600
